Here's a PlantUML sequence diagram representing the deployment and data flow of the system:

```plantuml
@startuml aurelien-m_raspberrypi-rustpy

participant "Web Browser" as Browser
participant "Rust Web Server" as WebServer
participant "Python Controller" as PythonController
participant "Rust Library" as RustLib
participant "Raspberry Pi Hardware" as Hardware

Browser -> WebServer: HTTP Request
activate WebServer

WebServer -> WebServer: Authenticate User

alt Authentication Successful
    WebServer -> Browser: Serve Web Interface
    Browser -> WebServer: WebSocket Connection
    activate Browser

    loop User Interaction
        Browser -> WebServer: Send LED Control Command
        WebServer -> PythonController: Forward Command
        activate PythonController

        PythonController -> RustLib: Call Hardware Functions
        activate RustLib

        RustLib -> Hardware: Control LEDs
        activate Hardware
        Hardware --> RustLib: Hardware Status
        deactivate Hardware

        RustLib --> PythonController: Operation Result
        deactivate RustLib

        PythonController --> WebServer: Update Status
        deactivate PythonController

        WebServer --> Browser: Real-time Update (WebSocket)
    end

    Browser -> WebServer: Close WebSocket
    deactivate Browser

else Authentication Failed
    WebServer -> Browser: Return Error
end

deactivate WebServer

@enduml
```